reviews.review_text: weak tape I really get lost in the echoes here. No doubt it is a good recording, but what it sounded like at MSG where this tape was made from leaves something to be desired.

agreed/disagreed I see what he's saying, but i still dug the hell out of this show. Crowd noise is audible throughout, which is cool with me, and the Pocky Way really gets the first set started.
Didn't dig Music Never Stopped.. something missing without Donna Jean.

Still, I downloaded this one, i recommend you do the same.
